OL,3,CReform's Pochin apologises after
OL,4,Chitting out at adverts 'full of black
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,FReform UK MP Sarah Pochin has
OL,8,Fapologised for any offence caused
OL,9,Fafter saying, "it drives me mad when I
OL,10,Fsee adverts full of black people, full
OL,11,Fof Asian people".
OL,13,FShe said her comments were "phrased
OL,14,Fpoorly" but insisted that many adverts
OL,15,Fare "unrepresentative of British
OL,16,Fsociety".
OL,18,FLabour said her comments were
OL,19,F"completely unacceptable" and called
OL,20,Fon party leader Nigel Farage to
OL,21,Fcondemn them.
