OL,3,CReform's Pochin apologises after
OL,4,Chitting out at adverts 'full of black
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,FThe Runcorn and Helsby MP was
OL,8,Fresponding to a viewer on TalkTV who
OL,9,Fcomplained about the demographics of
OL,10,Fadvertising.
OL,12,FThe MP said the viewer was "absolutely
OL,13,Fright" and "it drives me mad when I
OL,14,Fsee adverts full of black people, full
OL,15,Fof Asian people".
OL,17,FShe said: "It doesn't reflect our
OL,18,Fsociety, and I feel that your average
OL,19,Fwhite person, average white family
OL,20,Fis... not represented anymore."
