OL,7,FMs Pochin blamed the situation on the
OL,8,F"woke liberati" in the "arty-farty
OL,9,Fworld".
OL,11,F"It might be fine inside the M25, but
OL,12,Fit's definitely not representative of
OL,13,Fthe rest of the country," she said.
OL,15,FIn a later statement, she said she was
OL,16,Ftrying to say the advertising industry
OL,17,Fhad gone "DEI (diversity, equity and
OL,18,Finclusion) mad".
