OL,7,FShe said: "My comments were phrased
OL,8,Fpoorly and I apologise for any offence
OL,9,Fcaused, which was not my intention.
OL,11,F"The point I was trying to make is
OL,12,Fthat the British advertising agency
OL,13,Fworld have gone DEI mad and many
OL,14,Fadverts are now unrepresentative of
OL,15,FBritish society as a whole.
OL,17,F"I will endeavour to ensure my
OL,18,Flanguage is more accurate going
OL,19,Fforward."
