OL,10,Fcounting the numbers of people with a
OL,11,Fdifferent skin colour to her on TV
OL,12,Fadverts.
OL,14,F"Defining British people by the colour
OL,15,Fof their skin is completely
OL,16,Funacceptable and shows once again that
OL,17,FReform are more interested in dividing
OL,18,Four country than uniting it.
